transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Okay, thank you so much for calling customer service.

Speaker 2: How can I help you?

Speaker 1: Yes, I need to call about my RX 9922138.

Speaker 2: Thank you, your name and birthday?

Speaker 1: Steve Reeves, 9766.

Speaker 2: How can I help you?

Speaker 1: Right now, this is on an auto-fill and I need to take it off of auto-fill. I need to cancel that.

Speaker 2: Okay, let me go ahead and pause you out, and when you're ready to place an order for this medication or any of the other medications we offer, you can do so by calling in and place the order online with us or place the order over the phone with us, or you can do it online with the doctor that's assigned to you with the same insurance.

Speaker 1: Alrighty.

Speaker 2: Was there anything else I can assist you with?

Speaker 1: No problem, sir.

Speaker 2: No, that's all.

Speaker 1: Thanks.

Speaker 2: You're welcome, bye-bye.
